Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「比鄰星之冠」已經連接成功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.51,0:00:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認能量導管聯機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除持有第2類技術資格證以外的作業員
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.76,0:00:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請盡快退入附近的居住區
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 杜鵑同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經確認報酬了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和雷歐帕羅特之間的恩怨就這樣了結了吧 弁慶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.32,0:00:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 波拿帕羅特那傢伙 到底要糾結我的太陽能鏡到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.68,0:00:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也不難理解 因為畢竟是我的太陽能鏡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之現在先讓他們遠離
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.88,0:00:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲裡奧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.29,0:00:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.37,0:00:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子堂總帥 已經刻不容緩了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就去救那些被抓住的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:00:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.46,0:00:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀況已經改變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:01:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們和弁慶一起回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.88,0:01:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nerval現在應該從超時空跳躍的反應中推算出這個宙域了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.11,0:01:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被跟蹤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在責怪你們 你們回來真好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.52,0:01:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米裡奧君 殖民地內的非戰鬥人員全部都到避難所去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.98,0:01:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們以戰鬥狀態準備迎擊 同時進行雷歐帕羅特的修復
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.42,0:01:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「劍」的搜索呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.66,0:01:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們負責尋找那個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馮藏起來的「劍」只有風魔能找得到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用B.O.A.R.SHIP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.76,0:01:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長老 非常抱歉這麼緊急…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.41,0:01:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來你們沒事真太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能回到這裡是托了那邊的年輕人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和妹子的福
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.47,0:01:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.88,0:01:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高嶺！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:35.00,EDTITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(490,290)}{\fs45}{\fad(500,500)}密劍 閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弁慶那傢伙 竟然割了我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叛徒 竟然叛變到叛亂軍去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許可他四處旅行的是我 也許那正是他所追尋的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.17,0:03:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,途中發生什麼 有必要追查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在的問題是雷歐帕羅特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「比鄰星之冠」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很早以前就捨棄的據點現在要用來做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是想要取回來 50年前的那個力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 Enigma已經在我們這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈美的情況怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她在Enigma 睡在那個孩子旁邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有生命危險 但總是醒不來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss.高嶺不回來的理由就是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈美已經覺醒了 她本來所擁有的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anti-QT？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 是可以反轉QT的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nerval是知道這個所以把奈美…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們從神樂大人那裡繼承的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看透一切的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才的頭腦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anti-QT
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及…願望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然最後的鑰匙還是獅子堂秋葉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果讓雷歐帕羅特把力量取回了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說將成為無法挽回的威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫桑齊貝 破壞雷歐帕羅特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:04:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他正在修復中 現在追擊他應該無力反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss.阿蕾達 把Existent-Z交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將獅子堂秋葉帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nerval一定會以秋葉為目標攻來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高嶺 你來保護秋葉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 姐姐 我被Nerval…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不全是壞事 多虧這樣敵人的內情現在全清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後悔什麼的 就用你的劍來抹去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐帕羅特的修復完成後 就採取攻勢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了奪回奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 右轉舵 Mr.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將噴射器掘出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是點火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的東西要拿來做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像昨天吃過的那個呢 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 炸鯵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 覺得肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐帕羅特的秘密兵器？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是埋在隕石中 用納米機器人修理過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但竟然是必須用探寶棒來找 靈異科甘拜下風了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 Nerval他們的機器是找不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業工程 從A8到V21全部省略
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「劍」展開後 立即實裝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各部的調整推遲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在敵人攻過來之前不知能不能完工
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是…那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 妹子！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:06:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子堂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊…伊月
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子她…不在了的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法相信！怎麼可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子堂！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子堂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下站是雷歐帕羅特站前 雷歐帕羅特站前！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下站是…下站是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子 對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繪本真好呢 好像心靈都被洗滌了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是沒變 在做些蠢事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！你回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有軌電車 是你幹的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得好久沒來這裡了 也好久沒見你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 說起來是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾天房間太安靜了 我完全忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們不在…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煮芋頭怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子…說是死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我…因為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那個煮芋頭死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直讓我很不爽 成天毒舌我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣從今天開始我就可以高枕無憂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真差勁！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在說死了的人已經死了 這有什麼不對的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央監視台檢測出大規模的空間歪曲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:09:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人工智能殖民地！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全作業員暫時撤退 迎擊部隊 出擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.05,0:10:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次見面都發現你越來越窮酸了 雷歐帕羅特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 算了 等會再收拾你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先得先抓到小秋葉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫桑齊貝！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要立即實行修復作業 你們負責掩護B.O.A.R.SHIP
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫桑齊貝！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…小秋葉在哪兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.39,0:10:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越宇宙的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.65,0:11:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會將秋葉交給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高嶺姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我們…最後的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風音小姐 請看這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子堂她？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人已經攻入市內了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把地點傳給你了 拜託你保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這是我們的機體吧 烏魯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果還標著「ICP試用機」的話太不夠威猛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於同你再次對戰我無比遺憾 Miss.高嶺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:12:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi~ 住在雷歐帕羅特裡面的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住秋葉的人會得到最高級的箱子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…Existent-Z
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 秋葉前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了 獅子堂 找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音音子…菲裡奧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 這樣就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊月！我要進箱子裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子堂 如果你進入箱子就正中Nerval的下懷了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:12:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…進入箱子裡就會忘記討厭的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子的事也全都…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能不管你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.67,0:13:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是穿越宇宙的少女嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒了我就無法打倒Nerval嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…喜歡你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請振作起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉和妹子不都是真心…真心的關懷對方的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的你如果忘記了妹子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做那種過分的事…不是我喜歡的秋葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請站起來吧 秋葉 也為了妹子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊…伊月
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙…鯵！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 沒完沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蜜 那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民用機？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 沒有武裝在外面晃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.61,0:14:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被擊落的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 將我們送到雷歐帕羅特那
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又…又來上訪了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可已經克服了你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍了 雷歐帕羅特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小秋葉的事完了之後我會好好疼愛你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用對人工智能攻擊模式 哦呵呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子堂？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.45,0:15:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子堂！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是前輩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲裡奧？音音子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:16:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝我吧 我帶QT-Rose來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馮博士！你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼糟糕種子就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣Existent-Z的QT就不起作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃香？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少道個謝啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊月 保護秋葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃香…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have control！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始進行對接作業
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一太陽能鏡停止在對接位置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來開始實行第一輪連接作業
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完工並向第二太陽能鏡移動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在QT-Rose的有效圈內 大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二太陽能鏡開始連接作業
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完工後立即向第三太陽能鏡移動！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在抓住那小姑娘前不能好好的教訓雷歐帕羅特啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Existent-Z
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉由我來保護！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.35,0:17:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉去雷歐帕羅特那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個機體是…穗乃香嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:17:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神風！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們快走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三太陽能鏡連接完成 雷歐帕羅特修復完成！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全作業人員請立即從最近的入口退避到雷歐帕羅特殖民地裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於把所有部件全取回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐帕羅特修復 全工程完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業人員避難也完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓先頭部隊也全部撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐帕羅特 用「劍」一口氣把帳清算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 真的好好連接上了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽能鏡不能用 唉…這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馮說了 雷歐帕羅特的「劍」上有封印
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能解放雷歐帕羅特的力量的 只用黃金槍和秋葉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說妹子的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是我將你捲入命運之中 也許妹子不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜歡妹子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不打倒Nerval 還會有重要的人受傷死去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止Nerval 秋葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前我會保護秋葉 連著妹子的份一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.67,0:19:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會的 秋葉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊月…穗乃香…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真土
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那裝束是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是能勾起我想欺負你的心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐帕羅特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來解除你的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說封印？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了 穿越宇宙的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 認為自己一直沒有明白和Nerval戰鬥的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…只有我能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你做到的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓你得逞嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力的 和大家一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！雷歐帕羅特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卸裝！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣？這才是我的真正姿態！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.52,0:21:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來已經解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個垃圾！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫桑齊貝…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.00,0:21:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把律師叫過來 我要行使沉默權
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你 妹子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊月君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 即使這麼做…妹子也不會回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子不會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.85,0:21:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 妹子…妹子…已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子…妹子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你剛才說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我殺的？別說些容易引起誤會的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.79,0:22:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個煮芋頭還活著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.82,0:22:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Nerval大人那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.44,0:22:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹子…還活著？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:14.65,EDTITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(502,310)}終結的呼喊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.05,0:24:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,審判長 被告庫桑齊貝是無罪的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.09,0:24:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裁判員 說下意見
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.65,0:24:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有罪嗎？總覺得那個人很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.03,0:24:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我也是這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.20,0:24:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 就是有罪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.22,0:24:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我抗議！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:58.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡はいつでもそばにある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:08.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輝きたいよ　未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:24.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたの中　騒めくノイズは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:31.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馴れ愛の束縛　動けない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:38.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦しみが散らばる世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:43.99,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探して　失い、また求めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:49.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辿って　わたしの糸を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:53.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡は必然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.99,0:03:01.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと抱いてあげる　一雫の痛みも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:07.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯った証が　星になる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:14.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扉をあけて　飛べるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:58.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡一直就在我們身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:08.36,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想要發光 照亮未來…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:24.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你心中的 凌亂的雜音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:31.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是已熟知的愛的束縛 …動彈不得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:38.76,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦遍佈著這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:43.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找著… 失去，然後再次追求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:49.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追溯吧 沿著我的軌跡…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:53.95,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡必然會發生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.99,0:03:01.79,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄地將你抱住 不讓你有一點疼痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:07.75,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點亮的證明 成為了恆星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:14.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開門扉吧… 飛向天空！

Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.47,0:22:45.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甦る痛みに流されながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:54.58,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨って僕らはどこへ行くんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:23:08.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懐かしく暖かな空　その眩しい景色へ描いた幻は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:15.54,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揺れて消えた　遠く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.95,0:23:25.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解けぬ孤独を抱きながら　それでも祈ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.18,0:23:33.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰が同じ　希望の訪れが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.86,0:23:41.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇の破片が　絶えず僕の　胸に突き刺さる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.15,0:23:51.04,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君という光　ただ　知りたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.47,0:22:45.70,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在甦醒的痛苦中隨波逐流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:54.58,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨的我們不知要去往何方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:23:08.89,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那令人懷念地溫暖地天空 那種炫目地景色描繪出來的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:15.54,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖擺不定地消失 在遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.95,0:23:25.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被無法擺脫的孤獨抱住 我們也要祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.18,0:23:33.78,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都一樣 希望總會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.86,0:23:41.13,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗的碎片 無休止地 刺向我的胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.15,0:23:51.04,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想瞭解以你為名的光芒
